{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-130-composites-with-prime-repunit-property","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 130: Mešavina sa svojstvom Repunit broja osnovovanog na primbroju","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Broj koji se sastoji samo od cifre jedinica naziva se repunit. Definisemo $R(k)$ kao repunit dužine $k$; na primer, $R(6) = 111111$.</p>\n<p>Ako $n$ je pozitivan ceo broj i $GCD(n, 10) = 1$, može se pokazati da uvek postoji vrednost, $k$, takva da $R(k)$ je deljivo sa $n$, i neka je $A(n)$ najmanja vrednost $k$; na primer, $A(7) = 6$ i $A(41) = 5$.</p>\n<p>Dato je da za sve prime brojeve, $p > 5$, da $p − 1$ je deljivo sa $A(p)$. Na primer, kada je $p = 41, A(41) = 5$, i 40 je deljivo sa 5.</p>\n<p>Međutim, postoji nekoliko kombinacija za koje je i ovo tačno; prvih pet primera su 91, 259, 451, 481 i 703.</p>\n<p>Pronađi zbir prvih dvadeset pet vrednosti za $n$ takvo da $GCD(n, 10) = 1$ i $n − 1$ je deljivo sa $A(n)$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3ee1000cf542c50ff00","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301758,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-130-composites-with-prime-repunit-property"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function compositeRepunit() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\ncompositeRepunit();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>compositeRepunit()</code> treba da vrati <code>149253</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(compositeRepunit(), 149253);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-101-to-200","dashedName":"problem-130-composites-with-prime-repunit-property","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":true,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-131-prime-cube-partnership","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-129-repunit-divisibility","id":"5900f3ee1000cf542c50ff00","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-130-composites-with-prime-repunit-property"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}